{"id":47,"date":"2021-03-30T07:55:51","date_gmt":"2021-03-30T06:55:51","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/?page_id=47"},"modified":"2021-04-19T07:58:02","modified_gmt":"2021-04-19T06:58:02","slug":"cantina","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/identita\/cantina\/","title":{"rendered":"Cantina"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull has-background-dim\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-160\" alt=\"\" src=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-scaled.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" srcset=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-scaled.jpg 2560w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-scaled-600x400.jpg 600w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-768x512.jpg 768w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\">\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Cantina<\/h1>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left hero-highlight\">La particolarit\u00e0 della nostra cantina \u00e8 quella di trovarsi all&#8217;interno dell\u2019antica Barchessa. \u00c8 qui che innovazione e tradizione si mescolano. Accanto a nuove cisterne e tecnologie avanzate troviamo l\u2019applicazione dei vecchi metodi di vinificazione per riuscire a dar vita, anno dopo anno, a vini di qualit\u00e0.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-155\" srcset=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-scaled-600x400.jpg 600w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-768x512.jpg 768w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Non volevamo infatti stravolge l\u2019assetto originario dell\u2019edificio ma, al contrario, valorizzarne e conservare i suoi tratti caratteristici. Ecco cos\u00ec che vasche alte pi\u00f9 di 4 m sfiorano un soffitto di possenti travi in legno di pi\u00f9 di 400 anni.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p class=\"text-120\">L\u2019edificio costruito gi\u00e0 alla fine del \u2018400 non era stato concepito per accogliere al suo interno cisterne, torchi, botti e barrique, per cui i lavori di ristrutturazione avviati negli ultimi decenni hanno richiesto impegno, cura e precisione.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft size-medium\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" src=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/corina-rainer-sScNrKruEPs-unsplash-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-156\" srcset=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/corina-rainer-sScNrKruEPs-unsplash-200x300.jpg 200w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/corina-rainer-sScNrKruEPs-unsplash-scaled-600x900.jpg 600w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/corina-rainer-sScNrKruEPs-unsplash-683x1024.jpg 683w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/corina-rainer-sScNrKruEPs-unsplash-768x1152.jpg 768w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/corina-rainer-sScNrKruEPs-unsplash-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/corina-rainer-sScNrKruEPs-unsplash-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/corina-rainer-sScNrKruEPs-unsplash-scaled.jpg 1707w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft size-medium\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" src=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/adele-payman-2oYMwuFgnTg-unsplash-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-154\" srcset=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/adele-payman-2oYMwuFgnTg-unsplash-200x300.jpg 200w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/adele-payman-2oYMwuFgnTg-unsplash-scaled-600x900.jpg 600w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/adele-payman-2oYMwuFgnTg-unsplash-683x1024.jpg 683w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/adele-payman-2oYMwuFgnTg-unsplash-768x1152.jpg 768w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/adele-payman-2oYMwuFgnTg-unsplash-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/adele-payman-